function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	Hydra.ActorSetDisableWander(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetAIState(idActorSpawned, "aggressive")
	Hydra.ActorAddToBossEncounter(idActorSpawned)

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
		
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_RELIC_LOC, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_MARKER, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_RELIC_LOC, S_BURST_EFFECT)
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_RELIC_GIZMO, ID_RELIC_LOC)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, 1);	-- controls the travel time of each missile. Higher values means slower projectiles
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, 3); -- controls the spawn rate of the missiles (in missiles/second)
		
	idVFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, ID_MARKER, S_ATTRACTOR_VFX, true)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, idVFX)
		
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)


	idGizmo = idActorGizmo
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(ID_CHEST_SPAWNER)


end

end

function UF_PlayConvo_Beat(idPlayer)

	id_Player = idPlayer

	if j < 5 then
		if j == 1 then
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_BOSS_GRP_01, idPlayer, ID_BOSS_INVIS)
		end
		
		if j == 2 then
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_BOSS_GRP_02, idPlayer, ID_BOSS_INVIS)
		end
		
		if j == 3 then
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_BOSS_GRP_03, idPlayer, ID_BOSS_INVIS)
		end
		
		if j == 4 then
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_BOSS_GRP_04, idPlayer, ID_BOSS_INVIS)
		end	
	
		j = j + 1
	
	end	

end
